# flog
A simple $EDITOR blogging client.

## Requirements
- [Blog::Client](http://raa.ruby-lang.org/project/blogclient/)

## Synopsis
Run `flog` and edit the post template in $EDITOR. When done, save and exit
$EDITOR and your post will be submitted.

Alternatively, pass in your post as an argument or on stdin. 

`flog -h` for other options.

## Configuration 

    $ flog --dump-default-config > ~/.flogrc
    $ $EDITOR ~/.flogrc
